dc_title_s: Bridges and Tunnels, Mono County, California, 2019
dc_description_s: This dataset depicts bridges and tunnels within Mono County, CA. Both pedestrian bridges and automotive bridges are included in this dataset.. Last updated: 3/6/2019 This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
